Package: ubuntuscreenshot
Version: 0.2.6
Section: utils
Priority: extra
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: flowinginthewind700
Homepage: https://github.com/flowinginthewind700/ubuntuscreenshot
Conflicts: screenshot4ubuntu
Replaces: screenshot4ubuntu
Description: Screenshot tool for Ubuntu/GNOME
 A screenshot tool built with GPUI, designed for Ubuntu and GNOME desktops.
 .
 Features include:
  - System tray integration with camera icon
  - Multi-monitor support (dual screens)
  - Region selection with magnifier
  - In-selection annotation tools (pen, line, rectangle, ellipse, text)
  - Adjustable brush size, font size, and colors
  - Copy to clipboard or save to file
  - Chinese/English language support
Depends: libxcb1, libxkbcommon0, libxkbcommon-x11-0, xdg-desktop-portal, xdg-desktop-portal-gnome, x11-xserver-utils, zenity, libayatana-appindicator3-1, pipewire, libpipewire-0.3-0
Installed-Size: 35896
